long_description: Specifically designed for use with a Jetboil cooking system, this utensil set gives you a fork, spoon and spatula for all your camp kitchen needs. Utensils expand to reach deep into Jetboil cups; retract the utensils for compact storage in your Jetboil cup, pot or pan. Utensil shapes are optimized for the contours of Jetboil cups, pots and pans so you can easily get every last bite. Long extension works great with dehydrated meals in a bag, too! Durable nylon construction resists melting.
